ing: 1 (16 ounce) package weiners, cut into bite-size pieces
des: "Affordable, delicious and easy to make! Perfect for taking to gatherings or for those sports events and little fingers can't get enough of them!"
ins:
Mix wieners, ketchup, brown sugar, liquid smoke, Worcestershire sauce, and garlic powder together in a slow cooker.
Cook on Low for 2 to 4 hours.
